{
  "stem": "13079.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- so far as guarding was concerned, we had the London Poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The London Poles were not the Communist Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a whole flock of London Poles there who did police duty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so far as the individuals, the interrogators and the investigators, they were Americans, and some of them-- we had some from Holland and different countries that we employed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so far as numbers were concerned, what I tried to do was assemble a group that was compatible with each other, each member was, and had the brains and the know-how to try a case.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had in Dachau, I had a gentleman by the name of Peter Heller.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had Paul Goethe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Bill Lyons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And McKusky from Indiana.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- we-- we had that, but it was all within the limits of the pocketbook which was watched over by the War Crimes Branch of-- of the European Theater.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll have to explain that this way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The purpose of these trials was to obtain a judicial determination that these camps were criminal operations in their entirety, from the kommandant on down to the kapo.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that sense, we felt that it was necessary to have a representative from each segment of the camp's operation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, for example, we have representatives from the guards who did the work that you mentioned a moment ago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had doctors who were from a medical department.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had representatives from the Gestapo that had a branch there in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] every-- as I say, every activity was represented.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to have a large number of accused.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Dachau, for example, we had 40 accused.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Mauthausen, 61.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
